		<title>ATFX, ‘2021년도 가장 영향력 있는 10대 기업’ 선정</title>
		<link>https://www.atfx.com/ko/company-news/atfx-top10-most-influential-companies-of-the-year</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[ATFX]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Wed, 27 Oct 2021 04:37:00 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[기업 소식]]></category>
